  "notes": "背景：咖啡馆门口，傍晚，地面反光。氛围偏静，灯光暖黄。这是第一章的收尾场景。",
  "lines": [

    {
      "id": "s03_exit",
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "你们收拾好东西，走到咖啡馆门口。\n外面的空气凉了很多，路灯已经亮起来了。",
      "next": "s03_goodbye_setup"
    },

    {
      "id": "s03_goodbye_setup",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "kai",
      "emotion": "neutral",
      "text": "……方向呢。哪边。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s03_goodbye_setup2",
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "你说了你要去的方向。他点了点头，是另一个方向。",
      "next": "s03_player_skill_choice"
    },

    {
      "id": "s03_player_skill_choice",
      "type": "choice",
      "prompt": null,
      "affectionNote": "这是第一章结尾的最后一次主动选择。技能能直接撬动结局——不在 affection 范围内，但靠你自己决定。",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "A",
          "text": "下次还能在这家咖啡馆见你吗？",
          "label": "[直球]",
          "affectionDelta": 12,
          "skillUsed": { "id": "direct", "expGain": 3 },
          "setFlag": { "key": "kai_promise_made", "value": true },
          "next": "s03_kai_promise_react"
        },
        {
          "id": "B",
          "text": "路上小心。",
          "label": "[边界感]",
          "affectionDelta": 6,
          "skillUsed": { "id": "boundary", "expGain": 2 },
          "next": "s03_boundary_react"
        },
        {
          "id": "C",
          "text": "再见。",
          "affectionDelta": 3,
          "next": "s03_default_react"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "s03_kai_promise_react",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "kai",
      "emotion": "caught",
      "text": "……"
    },
    {
      "id": "s03_kai_promise_react2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "kai",
      "emotion": "warm",
      "text": "……可以。",
      "next": "s03_kai_promise_toast"
