      "emotion": "neutral",
      "text": "……再见。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s03_normal_end2",
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "他转身走了。\n走到路口，他回了一下头。\n你们的视线碰了一秒，他转回去，走了。",
      "next": "s03_chapter_end"
    },

    {
      "id": "s03_bad_end",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "kai",
      "emotion": "neutral",
      "text": "有事先走了。"
